    "original": "Keep it together! Any negative status effect with a finite duration (e.g. Bleeding, Charmed) has its duration reduced to [color=",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Keep it together! Any negative status effect with a finite duration (e.g. Bleeding, Charmed) has its duration reduced to [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.NegativeValue + \"]1[/color] turn. Status effects that have their effects grow weaker over several turns (e.g. Goblin Poison) are at their weakest state from the start.\""
